text: Gavril Maghiar (born 10 December 1926) is a Romanian former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Romanian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Romania Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bihor County
